&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Hybrid work structure -- 2 days/week in office&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Year 1 on-target earnings: $65,000&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Year 2 on-target earnings: $80,000&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;*On-target earnings include base salary, uncapped commissions, and bonuses.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Are you looking for a hybrid Inside Sales position in a flourishing industry with unlimited earning potential? Maybe you have been thinking about switching career paths and moving into sales? Hibu is here to set you up with best-in-class training so you can win and grow your career!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Start, or keep building, your sales career with a growing Digital Marketing company that helps small businesses across America grow and succeed. We are looking for career-driven, dynamic individuals who are money-motivated and excited about business-to-business sales.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Want to know more before going any further? Check out this short video of who we are, and we are sure you will want to explore further:&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;https://video.hibu.com/watch/HovfMuAyhhhUwShCo6eryi&quot;&gt;https://video.hibu.com/watch/HovfMuAyhhhUwShCo6eryi&lt;/a&gt;?&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;What you will be responsible for as an Account Executive:&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Grow a book of business by helping small businesses succeed with Hibu’s all-inclusive digital marketing platform, Hibu One&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Follow a proven &amp;amp; efficient prospecting process utilizing AI-driven tools that are designed to leverage personalization and simplify the sales process&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with a skilled Digital Marketing expert to deliver confident, consultative marketing recommendations to small businesses&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop long-term business relationships with your clients as you build your book of business (and earn ongoing residual commissions for retaining and increasing your clients!)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work within a wide variety of industries, making each day different!&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Selling in a highly productive and competitive environment to achieve and exceed sales objectives&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;Why our people love working at Hibu&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt; (and why we have made &lt;strong&gt;Power Selling’s Top 50 Companies to Sell&lt;/strong&gt; for &lt;strong&gt;EIGHT&amp;nbsp;years&lt;/strong&gt; in a row!):&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Flexibility and work-life balance&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Clear career path in both leadership and sales (Opportunities for promotion as early as 6 months into your career!)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Top-notch training and ongoing support&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Culture built around teamwork, continuing education, friendly competition, and fun&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partnership Selling Model&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Best-in-class digital marketing offerings&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Team building activities and recognition&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Medical, Dental, Vision, Life Insurance, and Disability Benefits&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Paid holidays, personal time, and vacation&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Community-focused organization&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Base Salary and Uncapped earnings through commission and bonus&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ongoing recognition and incentives, including an annual President’s Club Trip&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our &lt;strong&gt;core values&lt;/strong&gt; are something we live by every single day and what has helped to shape our business to become a leading provider of digital solutions, along with a company people love working for. Check out this &lt;strong&gt;video&lt;/strong&gt; to learn more about Hibu’s core values from our employees themse

